Empath::

"I said I could take care of myself!" Empath snarls, changing to 
rifle mode.  Suddenly a much smaller target, she drops like a stone 
as the phony Starscream's attack zings past harmlessly.  Reverting to 
robot mode, she gains altitude again and returns fire.  "I was a 
Seeker for eight million years, there's no way you'll get me to fall 
for any of their tricks!"
